Install ubuntu 20.04 LTS
Install ROS2 foxy base
Install Colcon 
update .bashrc - source, ros-domain-id 0
Clone repository with subrepositories
remove COLCON_IGNORE && build packages
cam - vision-msgs
lidar - libpcl-dev
      - cv-bridge, nav2-costmap-2d, pcl-conversions, vision-msgs, nav2-lifecycle-manager
      - Install LivoxSDK with -fPIC
      - livox-interfaces, livox-sdk-vendor, livox-driver
Enable deamons

Install ptplinux setup it
(enable and start service, edit config - slave, software) 
disable ntp (timedatectl)

sudo apt install openssh-server

set cyclonedds RMW (ros2 doctor --report)
Install cycloends
update .bashrc - export rmw
